organization known as B613?

30:37.670 --> 30:38.830
No.

30:38.830 --> 30:40.330
-No?
-No.

30:40.330 --> 30:42.420
Forgive me,
but I'm confused.

30:42.420 --> 30:44.420
I said that I created B613.

30:44.420 --> 30:47.500
I built it with my own
two hands, my own sweat,

30:47.500 --> 30:51.380
my own blood, but I did so
in response to a need.

30:51.380 --> 30:53.500
I did so because of you.

30:53.500 --> 30:54.790
Because of me?

30:54.790 --> 30:57.830
Well...uh...all of...you.

30:57.830 --> 31:02.170
The ones in charge.
The masters of the universe.

31:02.170 --> 31:05.380
White men whose complacency,
whose privilege

31:05.380 --> 31:08.920
