to molder, to decay.

31:14.620 --> 31:17.500
I was not born
with your privilege.

31:17.500 --> 31:20.040
I was taught to respect
the things that I had,

31:20.040 --> 31:23.000
to care for them,
to nurture them,

31:23.000 --> 31:28.170
which I have done
for the past 30 years.

31:28.170 --> 31:30.250
Nurture through
terrorist activity,

31:30.250 --> 31:31.960
through election rigging,

31:31.960 --> 31:33.880
through assassination
of foreign leaders?

31:33.880 --> 31:35.080
Yes.

31:37.120 --> 31:43.170
Senator, you asked if I alone
was responsible for B613.

31:43.210 --> 31:44.920
I was not.

31:44.920 --> 31:48.500
You bear that responsibility
with your privilege.

31:48.500 --> 31:52.670
What I am responsible for is
every decision to go to war,

31:52.670 --> 31:54.380
every President
sitting in office,

31:54.380 --> 31:56.880
every soldier brought
home in a casket,

31:56.880 --> 32:02.000
every citizen who sleeps free
and easy in their beds.

32:02.000 --> 32:05.290
I kept the stock market
afloat --

32:05.290 --> 32:07.540
the dollar where
it needs to be --

32:07.540 --> 32:09.880
our shores at peace.

32:09.880 --> 32:15.250
I am responsible for the fact
that this nation still stands.

32:15.250 --> 32:21.040
I wake up every morning
and I make America great.

32:21.040 --> 32:22.710
That is my legacy.

32:22.710 --> 32:25.540
