36:17.790 --> 36:19.830
For that, I am sorry.

36:19.830 --> 36:21.710
Prison's nothing.

36:21.710 --> 36:24.960
How's it go?

36:24.960 --> 36:26.880
"Freedom is never lost.

36:26.880 --> 36:30.290
I am always free.

36:30.290 --> 36:32.210
They can't cage me."

36:32.210 --> 36:34.960
[ Hushed ] No.

36:34.960 --> 36:38.210
They cannot cage you.

36:38.210 --> 36:41.620
♪♪

